00:51:11.080 --> 00:51:13.240
Why does it taste this
way or whatever?

00:51:13.240 --> 00:51:15.290
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: What's
your latest obsession?

00:51:15.290 --> 00:51:20.060
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: Well, lately
