very, very clean.

00:51:24.770 --> 00:51:31.950
I like this whole idea of making
breads out of cauliflower,

00:51:31.950 --> 00:51:35.200
figuring out all of
those kinds of things.

00:51:35.200 --> 00:51:37.970
But we've been traveling
a great deal.

00:51:37.970 --> 00:51:43.240
So I will be in the kitchen
