I know you can.

00:52:07.860 --> 00:52:09.620
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: But I like
the idea of having tthis food

00:52:09.620 --> 00:52:13.470
that is really, really clean
and done in a certain way

00:52:13.470 --> 00:52:18.920
