00:53:13.780 --> 00:53:17.730
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: You and I
are basically same generation,

00:53:17.730 --> 00:53:19.810
and I think when we were
coming up and forming some

00:53:19.810 --> 00:53:22.530
of our musical taste,
