00:53:22.530 --> 00:53:24.680 position:56%
a marketing term called world music.

00:53:24.680 --> 00:53:26.130
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: Yeah.

00:53:26.130 --> 00:53:29.340
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: And
so is that still a thing?

00:53:29.340 --> 00:53:30.640
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: I don't know.

00:53:30.640 --> 00:53:31.940
I think now it's global.

00:53:31.940 --> 00:53:34.080
Now it's just global.

00:53:34.080 --> 00:53:38.250
Everybody works with everybody
