00:53:45.140 --> 00:53:46.930
Do you look at Youtube?

00:53:46.930 --> 00:53:48.590 position:56%
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: Yeah, all of that.

00:53:48.590 --> 00:53:49.890
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: Is there --

00:53:49.890 --> 00:53:56.960
what do you think of the newer
