00:55:44.500 --> 00:55:45.800
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum:
That's a nice balance.

00:55:45.800 --> 00:55:47.400
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: And
that's what it is right now.

00:55:47.400 --> 00:55:51.780
It's all about balance.

00:55:51.780 --> 00:55:54.700
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: What's --
