00:55:54.700 --> 00:55:56.760
Your last recording won a Grammy.

00:55:56.760 --> 00:55:58.060
&gt;&gt; Dianne Reeves: Right, right.

00:55:58.060 --> 00:55:59.360
&gt;&gt; Larry Appelbaum: So
